beer.beer_description:
Here’s a mid-strength beer the brewers have thrown all their experience at to make sure you
get all the flavour of an Australian Pale Ale but with only 3.5% ABV. All Australian malts & hops contribute to a chewy pale malt body along with the tropical fruit & spice characters from Galaxy & Topaz hops. Eat, drink and be only slightly merry!
